{"tid":1293944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣傳】香港黑警撩人隻秋","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T02:33:51.000Z","uid":148482,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"404b1b1081ef3f4bf1a81b6c244619105b24bd19","tid":1293944,"uid":148482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:15:16.000Z","msg":"【真 ● 有牌爛仔】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ofOqiuTf3t4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FofOqiuTf3t4&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=296c9f28\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ofOqiuTf3t4</a><br />\n<br />\n「27星期的『學警基礎訓練課程』，包括<span style=\"color: red;\">法例</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警務程序</span>、警政社會學、警政心理學、步操、體能訓練、戰術、槍械和實習訓練等。」<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/15_recruit/training.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F15_recruit%2Ftraining.html&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=3c458bf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/15_recruit/training.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咁短時間嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">產物</span> 質素好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾次就見到呢班嘢唔多知<span style=\"color: red;\">「法例 &amp; 警務程序」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當權力落喺呢班人手上 真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4207598df04c6cc5dccd7464b80b4ac363670b32","tid":1293944,"uid":196114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"推 ！好撚離譜"},{"pid":"b0c27a3f37773aa6ba540aff19daa62bbfc18d58","tid":1293944,"uid":162330,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"推到到佢講我無嘢講"},{"pid":"53fb46a4b3fda00dde68212cccf1450511eda76c","tid":1293944,"uid":148482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited